{
  "stem": "1473.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can remember none in my family, other than the people in the apartment house or people that one-- at the market, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as for friends or acquaintances, there were no non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they must have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They must have gotten along well because there were not the pogroms that one heard of in Poland or Russia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was this kind of a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] living.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from what I read-- from the history, many Jews-- I mean, in the 19th century, Vienna was a very enlightened city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews prospered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews became very prominent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so that-- there must have been an atmosphere of tolerance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From all that I read, there was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On the other hand, there was a great-- whenever there is this ambience of tolerance, there's a great deal of assimilation that takes place so that many, many Jews-- Viennese Jews, and perhaps others, too-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] became wannabe Christians.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody changed their names.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was not America.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "People I don't think changed their names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I-- as for the, the interaction between non-Jews and Jews, I only know that from reading and history and not of personal--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From, from school, there were-- one of two girls, I can't remember their name, who would come to my apartment and who my mother allowed me to go to their apartment and play.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that, to me, was, was fine because I didn't have that many friends in, in the apartment house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I said, the girl was older.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the boy was of no interest to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We [LAUGHS] didn't play the same games.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
